    {
      "name": "GameText_24_Tutorial2 GameText_24_EnglishTutorialSection2",
      "entries": [
        {
          "key": 143,
          "value": " Social Stats"
        },
        {
          "key": 144,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Social Stat</color></b></style> \n\nThe way you respond will increase different <color=#cbadff>Social Stats</color>.\n\n<style=h3><b><color=#00FF66>*Tip*</color></b></style> \n<color=#cbadff>Social Stats</color> are what allow you to take your relationship with your confidant to the <color=green>next level</color>."
        },
        {
          "key": 146,
          "value": " <color=yellow>Elemental Gauge</color> is at the top left of the game screen. \nNext to the HP.\n"
        },
        {
          "key": 179,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Min Ultimate Skill</color></b></style> \n\nMin will save you from a fatal blow with her shield.\n\n<style=h3><b><color=#00FF66>*Tip*</color></b></style>\nThis skill can only be activated once a day."
        },
        {
          "key": 181,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Sia Ultimate Skill</color></b></style> \n\nSia will freeze <b>any enemy</b> with her ice powers."
        },
        {
          "key": 180,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Yuna Ultimate Skill</color></b></style> \n\nIf you fall in battle, Yuna will resurrect you.\n\n<style=h3><b><color=#00FF66>*Tip*</color></b></style>\nThis skill can only be activated once a day."
        },
        {
          "key": 182,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Barrier Breaking</color></b></style> \n\nUse your <color=#cbadff>Elemental Fist</color> to break through monsters that have barriers. Some barriers are stronger than others and may require several hits with the <color=#cbadff>Elemental Fist</color>. \n\n<style=h3><b><color=#00FF66>*Tip*</color></b></style>\nGet a boost to your <color=yellow>Elemental Gauge</color> by doing a <color=#00FFFF>Perfect Dodge</color>."
        },
        {
          "key": 801,
          "value": "White Essence"
        },
        {
          "key": 802,
          "value": "<style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>White Essence</color></b></style> \r\n\r\nYou gain <color=#00FFFF>White Essence</color> by training with your confidants. \r\n\r\n<style=h3><b><color=#00FF66>*Tip*</color></b></style>\r\nYou can <color=#cbadff>train</color> with your confidants at any time.\r"
        },
        {
          "key": 803,
          "value": "Black Essence"
        },
        {
          "key": 804,
          "value": "<style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Black Essence</color></b></style> \r\n\r\n<color=#00FFFF>Black Essence</color> allows you to unlock sword skills.\r\n\r\n<style=h3><b><color=#00FF66>*Tip*</color></b></style> You gather Black Essence by <color=#cbadff>finding it in dungeons</color> or <color=#cbadff>killing powerful monsters</color>.  "
        },
        {
          "key": 805,
          "value": "City Scavenging"
        },
        {
          "key": 806,
          "value": "<style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Scavenging & Combat Stats</color></b></style> \r\n\r\nYou can increase certain <color=#00FFFF>Combat Stats</color> by going to the city and scavenging. \r\nDepending on what <i>character you choose</i>, different stats will be increased. \r\n\r\n<style=h3><b><color=#00FF66>*Tip*</color></b></style>\r\nYou can <color=#cbadff>Go Scavenging</color> with the character by talking to them at night.\r"
        },
        {
          "key": 818,
          "value": "<style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Perfect Dodge Reminder</color></b></style> \r\n\r\nDodging <i>right before</i> an enemy attack triggers <color=#00FFFF><b>Slows Down</b></color> .\r\n\r\nUse  {ButtonSouth}  <i>right before</i> enemy attacks.\r"
        }
      ]
    },
