    {
      "name": "GameText_26",
      "entries": [
        {
          "key": 154,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Breathe Training</color></b></style> \n\nControl your breathing by pressing {ButtonSouth}. Every breath you take will subtract numbers from your “total”. \n\nYour goal is to reach an even 0. If you fall below zero, your “breath” will not be counted."
        },
        {
          "key": 155,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Squat Session</color></b></style> \n\nPress the buttons shown in the right order in order to perform squats. After a while, the buttons will disappear and you will have to push the buttons based on the movements you make.\n\nShow Min that you deserve to be her coach by doing more squats than her!"
        },
        {
          "key": 156,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Cell Dividing</color></b></style> \n\nSplit up the cells into their correct categories!\n\n<color=red>red cells</color> go to the <b>left</b>.\n\n<color=blue>blue cells</color> go to <b>right</b>!"
        },
        {
          "key": 157,
          "value": " <style=Title><b><color=#9a75ff>Meditation</color></b></style> \n\nClick on good “thoughts” while trying to avoid clicking on bad “thoughts”!"
        },
